gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Ah, hello there!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the wonderful world of\n"
	.string "Pokémon!\p"
	.string "My name is Professor Eiji Sanzashi,\n"
	.string "and I'm thrilled to be your guide as you\l"
	.string "embark on your adventure through the\l"
	.string "Toshou region.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This is one of the many Pokémon that\n"
	.string "inhabit this world.\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "Pokémon are fascinating creatures,\n"
	.string "each with their own unique abilities and\l"
	.string "characteristics.\p"
	.string "Some live in the wild, others by our side\n"
	.string "as partners.\p"
	.string "Together, humans and Pokémon build a\n"
	.string "world full of adventure and discovery.\p"
	.string "However, there is still much we do not\n"
	.string "know about Pokémon.\p"
	.string "That's why I study them, to learn more\n"
	.string "about their mysteries.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "But before we dive into the excitement,\n"
	.string "let's get to know a little more about\n"
	.string "you!$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "What do you look like?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "I see.\n"
	.string "And what's your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "{PLAYER}{KUN}, is it?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Oh! You're {PLAYER}{KUN} from next door,\n"
	.string "right?\p"
	.string "You're the one who recently moved to\n"
	.string "Everwood Town.\p"
	.string "I've been excited to meet you!\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "The Toshou region is filled with diverse\n"
	.string "environments--from serene forests to\l"
	.string "bustling cities, and from quiet villages\l"
	.string "to vast mountain ranges.\p"
	.string "As you journey through these lands,\n"
	.string "you'll encounter many Pokémon and\l"
	.string "people, each with their own story to\l"
	.string "tell.\p"
	.string "But every journey begins with a single\n"
	.string "step, and today, you'll take yours.\p"
	.string "The world of Pokémon is vast and full of\n"
	.string "surprises.\p"
	.string "Your adventure is about to begin,\n"
	.string "{PLAYER}{KUN}. Are you ready?\p"
	.string "Go forth, and let your journey unfold!\p"
	.string "$"

